Package: HEXmatchR
Type: Package
Title: Match University Organisations to GERIT with Tidyverse and Ellmer
Version: 0.5.3
Author: Malte Hückstädt
Maintainer: Malte Hückstädt <malte.hueckstaedt@stifterverband.de>
Description: Prepares scraped university organisation data, generates GERIT
    candidates, asks OpenAI models for structured matching decisions through
    ellmer, and writes compact matching outputs that can be merged back into
    course data.
License: Stifterverband-intern
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
